    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/ba45505e4beee5c3cc4d9ca1a30be783.apng?t=1755218068\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/ba45505e4beee5c3cc4d9ca1a30be783.poster.avif?t=1755218068\" class=\"bb_img\" alt=\"在星际资本主义的废墟里挣扎求生\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跻身 2022 年最受好评的独立游戏之列、曾获 TGA 提名的《深空梦里人》，是一款受桌游启发的叙事角色扮演游戏。故事发生在“厄灵之眼”，这一破败的空间站是千万人的家园，人人都在跨星系的资本主义社会边缘挣扎求生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人造躯壳里装着数字意识——你就是所谓的“梦游体”，曾归某个大型集团所有，现在他们又想将你召回。想要见证下一个循环，就得和厄灵之眼上形形色色的陌生面孔打交道，斡旋于不同势力之间，结交好友，维持生计，在这个怪奇都市生存下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/fd1d3313989bd4f962d8e117d5c45243.poster.avif?t=1755218068\" aria-label=\"Completing an action\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/fd1d3313989bd4f962d8e117d5c45243.webm?t=1755218068\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/fd1d3313989bd4f962d8e117d5c45243.mp4?t=1755218068\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/8fe8922c7e32a41eacc22e8e81ded602.apng?t=1755218068\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/8fe8922c7e32a41eacc22e8e81ded602.poster.avif?t=1755218068\" class=\"bb_img\" alt=\"ROLL THE DICE. DO THE WORK. GET PAID. SURVIVE.\" width=600 height=54 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作自桌游汲取灵感，引入“骰子”、“时钟”与“动因”要素，旨在让玩家自主选择前进路线，搭配内容丰富、互动及时的世界塑造，带来玩家主导的游戏体验。日夜循环之间，你必须用骰子来决定如何度日。携手共进或是斩断连结，你的目标都是揭开真相，摆脱猎人，笑到最后，甚至逆转过去！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/4b9e4a64e0f1608631852ca2290a699e.poster.avif?t=1755218068\" aria-label=\"Different characters living on Erlin&#039;s Eye\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/4b9e4a64e0f1608631852ca2290a699e.webm?t=1755218068\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/4b9e4a64e0f1608631852ca2290a699e.mp4?t=1755218068\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/1acce9d0fad1ec5ffb8e524a7058dcb0.apng?t=1755218068\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/1acce9d0fad1ec5ffb8e524a7058dcb0.poster.avif?t=1755218068\" class=\"bb_img\" alt=\"如约赴会\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各行各业都想在星辰间挣扎求生，空间站则来者不拒：清运工、工程师、黑客、酒保、街头食品小贩，大家为何齐聚此处，那就说来话长了。向谁伸出援手，都由你自己决定，好友携起手来，就能合力改变未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/92a24adeaad07a26c94de2557eb00813.poster.avif?t=1755218068\" aria-label=\"Hacking into a node\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/92a24adeaad07a26c94de2557eb00813.webm?t=1755218068\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/92a24adeaad07a26c94de2557eb00813.mp4?t=1755218068\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/56dd63cad02c055203a49045b817777e.apng?t=1755218068\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/56dd63cad02c055203a49045b817777e.poster.avif?t=1755218068\" class=\"bb_img\" alt=\"窥探秘密\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最终，骰子将成为黑入空间站云端的绝佳工具，过往数十年的数据任你浏览，新区域也揭开神秘面纱，还有更多秘密静待解锁。这可是你的独家本领，能不能逆转未来，在此一举。敢于深入空间站网络空间深处的人啊，无数集团秘密、失控人工智能，以及失落的数据信息，都等你来发掘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/e877407fc14b5874b661ac713a1a49df.poster.avif?t=1755218068\" aria-label=\"Character classes selection screen\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/e877407fc14b5874b661ac713a1a49df.webm?t=1755218068\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/e877407fc14b5874b661ac713a1a49df.mp4?t=1755218068\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/28c40a12345492e54793cdf7903e952a.apng?t=1755218068\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/28c40a12345492e54793cdf7903e952a.poster.avif?t=1755218068\" class=\"bb_img\" alt=\"在劫难逃\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在埃森-阿普眼里，你不过是公司的所有物，星际生意中的一件小小资产。在这个宇宙里，人类的扩张充斥着压榨与剥削，孕育你的那个系统自然也毫无怜悯之心可言。公司赋予的躯壳日渐腐朽，是时候摆脱控制，在天马行空的科幻世界里闯出自己的一条路，探讨何为不确定性、人格与自由。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/3341d7393ccb3cfb69ad9365094a5fb9.apng?t=1755218068\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/3341d7393ccb3cfb69ad9365094a5fb9.poster.avif?t=1755218068\" class=\"bb_img\" alt=\"桌游灵感\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《深空梦里人》引入“骰子”、“时钟”与“动因”要素，旨在让玩家自主选择前进路线，搭配内容丰富、互动及时的世界塑造，带来玩家主导的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/273880e8b4c099db8d55ce3acba7a42a.avif?t=1755218068\" alt=\"动作骰子\" width=600 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个循环，你都要掷出骰子，为空间站上花样百出的行动分配不同的点数。靠着这一个个行动，你将抉择何事、何人对你最为重要，从而塑造身边人的生活，并最终影响空间站的未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/cb0a62f6dcbb40845346152008bfecb3.avif?t=1755218068\" alt=\"时钟滴答\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时钟记录着你乃至空间站上众人的行动。从成为远眺酒吧的常驻成员，到保护朋友不被亚特坎治安兵追杀，有了时钟，就既能追踪自己的足迹，又能了解一举一动在身边世界泛起的涟漪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/de21e1aa8b546d34ecda430ed0aecf0a.avif?t=1755218068\" alt=\"动因 + 技能\" width=600 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你要完成的不是任务，而是“动因”——挑选和抉择对你举足轻重的故事和活动，就靠它来引导。追踪动因，就能磨练角色的五项技能（机械、界面、耐久、直觉及投入），解锁各种特长和奖励，反映或改变你要在这个世界上如何生存下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/05e08881f9d970b523d85359d76bf726.apng?t=1755218068\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/05e08881f9d970b523d85359d76bf726.poster.avif?t=1755218068\" class=\"bb_img\" alt=\"完整体验\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《深空梦里人》共有三个于发售后推出的 DLC 章节——《浪涌》《避难》《清除》，如今都将包含在游戏的现行版本中。这三章将拓宽游戏世界，还会向厄灵之眼加入额外角色和地点，为游戏后期引入精彩纷呈的全新剧情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/25fc0f18a508bf2b091100aef5a9a3db.apng?t=1755218068\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/25fc0f18a508bf2b091100aef5a9a3db.poster.avif?t=1755218068\" class=\"bb_img\" alt=\"梦游体 快醒醒\" /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于开发者</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578650/extras/33502000760418a22bb1b94dae37daa5.avif?t=1755218068\" alt=\"Jump Over the Age\" width=600 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump Over the Age 是由 Gareth Damian Martin（they/them）创立的一人团队游戏开发工作室。Gareth 曾获 GDCA 和 IndieCade 奖项肯定，亦拿下 TGA 提名、多项 IGF 提名、GDC 提名和四项 BAFTA 提名，并被评为“杰出的游戏世界创造者”（《Edge》杂志）、跻身“最激动人心的独立游戏之星”之列（Eurogamer）。</p>",
